title: Sample Book (United Kingdom), 1820–50
description: Sample book with a marble printed cover and a green suede back strip containing samples of printed cotton textiles in various colors which are pasted on paper sheets.

tombstone.epitaph: Sample Book (United Kingdom), 1820–50; cardboard, leather, paper, cotton; H x W: 22.6 x 33.1 cm (8 7/8 x 13 1/16 in.); Gift of Seymore DeRicci; 1921-9-1
